---
title: Easy American Beef Chilli & Rapid Rice with Cheddar Cheese & Corn Chips
description: Gather round, come one and all – it’s chilli night! We're giving it a taste of the deep South with our Louisiana spice blend cooked
into the hearty bean and veggie filling, plus added crispy corn chips so you can feel good about digging into this flavourful feast.
